{"thag6.12:0.1":"Theragatha 6.12 ","thag6.12:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.12:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.12:0.4":"Brahmadattattheragatha ","thag6.12:1.1":"“Akkodhassa kuto kodho, ","thag6.12:1.2":"dantassa samajivino; ","thag6.12:1.3":"Sammadannavimuttassa, ","thag6.12:1.4":"upasantassa tadino. ","thag6.12:2.1":"Tasseva tena papiyo, ","thag6.12:2.2":"yo kuddham patikujjhati; ","thag6.12:2.3":"Kuddham appatikujjhanto, ","thag6.12:2.4":"sangamam jeti dujjayam. ","thag6.12:3.1":"Ubhinnamattham carati, ","thag6.12:3.2":"attano ca parassa ca; ","thag6.12:3.3":"Param sankupitam natva, ","thag6.12:3.4":"yo sato upasammati. ","thag6.12:4.1":"Ubhinnam tikicchantam tam, ","thag6.12:4.2":"attano ca parassa ca; ","thag6.12:4.3":"Jana mannanti baloti, ","thag6.12:4.4":"ye dhammassa akovida. ","thag6.12:5.1":"Uppajje te sace kodho, ","thag6.12:5.2":"avajja kakacupamam; ","thag6.12:5.3":"Uppajje ce rase tanha, ","thag6.12:5.4":"puttamamsupamam sara. ","thag6.12:6.1":"Sace dhavati cittam te, ","thag6.12:6.2":"kamesu ca bhavesu ca; ","thag6.12:6.3":"Khippam nigganha satiya, ","thag6.12:6.4":"kitthadam viya duppasun”ti. ","thag6.12:6.5":"… Brahmadatto thero …. "}